- [ ] UUID validation works correctly
- [ ] Session ID extracted from filename
- [ ] Session ID injected into stdout with prefix
- [ ] 10 minute timeout implemented
- [ ] Resume flag added when session ID provided
- [ ] Error handling for missing/invalid log files
- [ ] Unit tests for UUID validation and polling logic
- [ ] Integration test with real Copilot CLI (if available)

